Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.45,0:00:22.59,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,闭上双眼用心去感受
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.20,0:00:29.79,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,满溢的热气
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.03,0:00:33.75,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,答案就在心中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.13,0:00:40.64,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,那一日的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.64,0:00:43.59,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,并非偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.91,0:00:49.76,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,苏醒的追忆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.13,0:00:52.86,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,katharsis
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.18,0:00:57.95,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,解放吧 将一切解放
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.22,0:01:00.99,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,朝着未来跑动起来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.99,0:01:03.97,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,名为青涩和你的冲动
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.97,0:01:06.92,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,现在立刻就传达到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.20,0:01:09.35,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,强而有力地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.75,0:01:14.32,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,朝那倾洒而出的光芒 伸出双手
